summary: An ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 59669 and authorizing the return of portion of earnest money deposited for the purchase of Lots 7, 8, 12, Block 2; and Lots 16, 17, 18, 19, Block 8; and Lot 9, Block 12, and the East half of Lot 13, and all of Lot 14, Block 13, and that portion of Tract B, Block 13, lying between West line of East half of Lot 13 and East line of Lot 14, Block 13, extended Northeasterly to West Barton Street, all in Fauntleroy Addition; and Lot 7, Block 2, Adam's 1st Addition to Fauntleroy Park.
